<div class="whole-page-wrapper">
	<%= render 'shared/score_menu' %>
	<div class="whole-page left-section" style="background-color:#fff">
		
		<script type="text/javascript">

					var pie_vote_real;
	
					$(document).ready(function() {
						Highcharts.setOptions({
						    colors: ['#007236', '#9e0b0f','#f7941d']
						});


						pie_vote_real = new Highcharts.Chart({
							chart: {
									 renderTo: 'pie-vote-real',
									 backgroundColor: '#fff',
							         plotBackgroundColor: null,
							         plotBorderWidth: null,
							         plotShadow: false
							      },
							      title: { text: '' },
							      tooltip: {
							         formatter: function() { var s; if (this.point.name) { s = this.y; } return s; }
							      },
							      plotOptions: {
							         pie: {
							            allowPointSelect: true,
							            cursor: 'pointer',
							            dataLabels: {
							               enabled: false
							            },
							            showInLegend: true
							         }
							      },
									legend:{ backgroundColor: '#fff' },
							       series: [{
							         type: 'pie',
							         name: 'Votes on real tweets',
							         data: [
							            ['Correct', <%= Vote.vote_real_correct(current_user) %>],
							            ['Incorrect', <%= Vote.vote_real_incorrect(current_user) %>]
							         ]
							      }]
						});

					
					});

				</script>
		<div id="pie-vote-real" style="width:225px; height:225px;"></div>
	</div>
	<div class="whole-page middle-section">
		<h3>Ranking in <%= current_user.school.name%></h3>
		<% @school_leaderboard.each do |user| %>
			<div>
				<span style="float:right"><%= user.position_in_school_my_votes_real %> (<%= user.score_my_vote_real %>)</span>
				<%= user.name %>
			</div>
		<% end %>
		<hr />
		<h3>Ranking on Twittest</h3>
	
	</div>
	<div class="whole-page right-section">
		<h3>This Section</h3>
		<p>
			This chart show your progress on correctly identifying when someone is tweeting as themselves.
		</p>
		<hr />
		<h3>Tips</h3>
		<p>
			Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipiscing elit. Quisque gravida mi eget est 
			vestibulum hendrerit. Quisque tempor dolor eget quam volutpat venenatis. Vestibulum 
			ante ipsum primis in faucibus orci luctus et ultrices posuere cubilia Curae; Cum sociis 
			natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus.
		</p>
	</div>
</div>